      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The shell decides whether this serve authors a repo theme or consumes the locked default, coordinates browser settings with the theme routes, and applies the resolved runtime layer to the document. Those decisions belong to the app because they combine invocation flags, browser storage, DOM state, and server persistence. The token, folder, and override contracts live in "
